com.sun.source.tree.TreeVisitor<java.lang.Object,MethodModel>
public class ModelFactoryJavaMethodUtils
extends com.sun.source.util.TreeScanner<java.lang.Object,MethodModel>

Carries out some token visitation outside of the compiling task that calculates the total number of statements in each method and the number of independent code paths though each.
